# Link Maintenance and Validation Rules

## Internal Link Standards
All internal links within the repository MUST follow these patterns:

### Relative Path Format
- Use relative paths starting with `../` or `./`
- Never use absolute paths or hardcoded URLs for internal content
- Format: `[Link Text](../path/to/file.md)`

### Cross-Reference Tracking
When editing any file, check for these common link patterns:

#### Security References
- `../standards/security.md` - Referenced from multiple responsible-practices pages
- `../responsible-practices/security.md` - Referenced from feature development pages

#### API Documentation Links  
- `../apis/README.md` - Main API overview
